body:
## Environment

- OS: macOS Sierra (10.12.3)
- rustc: `rustc 1.17.0-nightly (ea7a6486a 2017-02-04)`
- cargo: `cargo 0.17.0-nightly (385e243 2017-01-27)`
- Target code base: Servo (https://github.com/servo/servo/commit/cd63f1b158807035d2a83584e64329015a3fff4d)

## Tracking issue on Servo side.

- https://github.com/servo/servo/issues/15391


## Step to Reproduce

- Try to build servo's repository (`./mach build --dev --verbose`)
- This problem is reproducible on both cases:
  - Full build.
  - Complete to build once on non-incremental build, and edit some files under `/component/style/`.
